{"tid":642282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連先達舖頭都加入埋黃牛戰團","createTime":"2018-04-25T16:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T17:28:17.000Z","uid":167573,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"987cf29ae8997d72af38bafa5eec7bd7f2627c66","tid":642282,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"雖然黃子華已經親自拍片呼籲大家唔好買賣黃牛，但係成效似乎就唔太大，今日所見，有唔少人將大量嘅棟篤笑門票放喺網上發售炒賣。有一間位於先達嘅手機店，今晚喺佢哋個fb page貼咗張「磚頭飛」相片，caption係「今日戰績」，都係黃子華棟篤笑嘅門票，日期分別係7月6、21、27同28，仲有一疊最厚嘅，角度問題睇唔到日期。<br />\n呢疊「戰績」究竟係點得嚟呢？Post上fb又想點呢？拿，有網民就留言話：「黃子華呼籲，寧願個位吉都唔好益黃牛！」、「關公都幫你唔到」，但亦有網民留言話：「要三張吖唔該！」馬上有另一網民回覆：「唔好幫襯黃牛！」仲將呢個post share咗去黃子華嘅官方fb專頁。<br />\n一小時之後，即約晚上十點幾，呢間手機舖就刪post，拒再同大家分享佢嘅「今日戰績」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180425/58118353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58118353&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb30%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=92312aa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58118353&h=c6de5632\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180425/58118353</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無非都係想差人同海關再去做嘢啫.<br />\n<br />\n今次俾人cap哂圖.  <br />\n<br />\n唔知可以去邊個部門舉報？<br />\n<br />\n警察? 康民署?"},{"pid":"203e01809c34e75fd88a0bced115de724fb89fe8","tid":642282,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"現行法例 唔係話郁黃牛唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edc8262d5cec49421691ae1b7b1713dc804bdf7","tid":642282,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"203e01809c34e75fd88a0bced115de724fb